<head>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/styles/home-page.css" />
</head>

<div class="container mt-4 p-4" style="background-color: rgba(169, 255, 169, 0.7); border-radius: 16px;">

  <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-between">
   
    </div>
  

  <div class="d-flex flex-column align-items-center my-4 min-vh-40">
    <div class="container-fluid">

      <div class="row g-0">
        <div class="col-md-6 d-flex align-items-center">
          <div class="card-body p-3 mx-2">
            <h2 class="card-title my-4">Island Page</h2>
            <p class="card-text p-3" style="font-size: 20px;">"Dodo birds were dumb," 

said some random people.

"Dodo birds were dumb?"

asked some brilliant minds.

​

In a fluffy world where we’re all dodos... How cute would that be? Very cute!!! But alas, the sailors and invasive species just won’t leave us alone. Ughhh.

​

What's a dodo to do???

Reclaim our habitat with courage, wisdom, and a little bit of dodo magic!!! 

​

Game on...
            </p>

          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="col ">
          <img
            src="/images/backPixel.avif"
            class="img-fluid"
            alt="Placeholder Image"
            style="border-radius: 16px;"
          />
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p>

    </p>
    <div class="d-flex align-items-center justify-content-center my-4">
      {{#if myIsland}}
        <a href="/my-island" class="btn btn-primary" style="background-color: #FF6600; border: 1px solid #FF6600 ; font-size: 25px; padding:10px 30px 10px 30px; border-radius: 25px;">Check my island</a>
      {{else}}
        <a href="/island-form" class="btn btn-success" style="font-size: 30px; padding:10px 30px 10px 30px; border-radius: 25px; ">Create my island</a>
      {{/if}}
    </div>
    <div class="d-flex align-items-center flex-column mb-3">

      <h2>Scroll down to see more</h2>
      <div class="arrow">
        &#8595;
        <!-- Down arrow symbol -->
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
<div class="container mt-4 p-4" style="background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); border-radius: 16px;">
     <div class="row ">
      <div class="col-md-6 offset-md-3">
        <form class="d-flex" action="/island-search" method="GET">
          <input
            class="form-control me-2"
            type="search"
            placeholder="Search"
            aria-label="Search"
            name="q"
            id="search"
            style="  border-radius: 25px;"
          />
          <button class="btn btn-outline-primary" type="submit" style=" padding:10px 30px 10px 30px; border-radius: 25px;">Search</button>
        </form>
      </div>

  <div class="row row-cols-1 row-cols-md-3 g-4 min-vh-100">
    {{#each islands as |island|}}
      <div class="col">
        <div class="card" style="background-image:url('/images/island.themes/{{island.theme}}.jpg'); border-radius: 16px;  background-position: center; background-size: cover;  ">

          <div class="card-body" style="  border-radius: 20px; ">
            <div class="p-4 my-3" style="background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.557); border-radius:16px;">
            <h5 class="card-title" style="color: white;">{{island.name}}</h5>
            <p class="card-text" style="color: white;">{{island.theme}}</p>

            </div>
            <a
              href="/island-explore/{{island.id}}"
              class="btn btn-success"
              style="border-radius: 16px;"
            >Check this island</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    {{/each}}

  </div>
</div>

